1
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:17,320
새벽 네 시 모니터 하나 켜놓고
At 4 AM, with one monitor turned on,

2
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:19,620
줄줄이 코드를 써 내려가
I write down lines of code.

3
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:23,356
에러 백 개쯤 지우고 나면
After deleting about a hundred errors,

4
00:00:23,469 --> 00:00:26,320
캐릭터 하나가 눈을 떠
A character opens its eyes.

5
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:30,719
아무도 모르는 이 작은 세계
This small world, known to no one,

6
00:00:30,719 --> 00:00:33,497
내 손끝에서 태어나는 중
Is being born from my fingertips.

7
00:00:33,826 --> 00:00:37,479
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams within the pixels,

8
00:00:37,479 --> 00:00:40,280
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one square at a time.

9
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:44,340
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through the buggy night,

10
00:00:44,340 --> 00:01:02,380
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My own game begins.

11
00:01:02,380 --> 00:01:04,780
스프라이트 하나 그려 넣으면
When I draw in a single sprite,

12
00:01:04,924 --> 00:01:07,465
작은 세상이 움직이잖아
The small world starts to move.

13
00:01:08,569 --> 00:01:12,200
혼자서 다 해야 하는 밤이
The night when I have to do everything by myself

14
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,269
오히려 나를 웃게 만들어
Rather makes me smile.

15
00:01:14,390 --> 00:01:19,299
완성 버튼을 누르는 그날
On the day I press the complete button,

16
00:01:19,299 --> 00:01:22,099
온 세상이 플레이하게 될 거야
The whole world will play it.

17
00:01:22,677 --> 00:01:25,459
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams within the pixels,

18
00:01:25,459 --> 00:01:28,319
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one square at a time.

19
00:01:29,944 --> 00:01:32,260
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through the buggy night,

20
