My own game begins.

21
00:01:57,459 --> 00:01:59,799
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams within the pixels,

22
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:02,691
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, one square at a time.

23
00:02:03,569 --> 00:02:06,620
언젠가 누군가 플레이할 때
Someday, when someone plays it,

24
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:09,180
이 밤의 코드가 빛이 돼
The code of this night will become light.

